        <mxCell id="legend-text" value="This master diagram provides a bird's-eye view of the entire Autonomous QA system, showing how 14 major flows interconnect across core execution, AI analysis, data management, system monitoring, and security/compliance domains.&#xa;Each flow is documented in detail in its own Draw.io diagram (01-14) with swim lanes, state transitions, error handling, and service interactions. The system follows industry best practices (SOLID, 12-Factor App, OWASP Top 10) and is production-ready with comprehensive observability, horizontal scalability, and complete audit trails.&#xa;&#xa;Color Coding: Green = Execution | Purple = AI | Orange = Data Management | Blue = System/Monitoring | Red = Security/Compliance | Brown = Database | Yellow = Metrics" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=6.5;" vertex="1" parent="1">
