        <mxCell id="metadata-text" value="Project: Autonomous QA - AI-Powered Test Automation Platform | Tech Stack: Node.js 20 + TypeScript 5 + React 18 + PostgreSQL 16 + Prisma 5 + Playwright | Architecture: Modular services, atomic transactions, event-driven, real-time WebSocket, stateless JWT auth&#xa;Diagrams Created: 14 detailed flow diagrams (500+ nodes total, 90+ swim lanes) | Documentation: PROJECT_OVERVIEW.md, ERD.md, DIAGRAM_COMPARISON.md, README.md | Created: December 2025 | Version: 1.0 Production-Ready&#xa;Industry Patterns: Google SRE, AWS Well-Architected, 12-Factor App, SOLID principles, DDD, Event Sourcing, CQRS, Circuit Breaker, Retry/Fallback, Advisory Locks, RBAC, OAuth2/JWT, SOC 2 / GDPR / HIPAA compliance" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=5.5;fontColor=#ffffff;" vertex="1" parent="1">
